What are the values of `p` and `q` after the following code executes?

```java
int a = 9;
int b = 4;
double p = a / b;
double q = (double) a / b;
```

What is the value of `result` after the following code executes?

```java
double d = 5.99;
int result = (int) d;
```

What are the values of `x` and `y` after the following code executes?

```java
double val = 3.6;
int x = (int) val * 2;
int y = (int)(val * 2);
```

What is printed as the result of the following code?

```java
int n = Integer.MAX_VALUE;
System.out.println(n + 1);
```

What is printed as the result of the following code?

```java
int a = 4;
int b = 3;
System.out.println("Result: " + a + b);
System.out.println(a + b + " total");
```

What is the value of `avg` after the following code executes?

```java
int total = 17;
int count = 5;
double avg = 0.0;
avg += total / count;
```

A student writes the following code to compute the percentage of quiz questions answered correctly.

```java
int correct = 17;
int total = 20;
double percentage = correct / total * 100;
```

The student expects `percentage` to be `85.0`, but the stored value is different. Which of the following identifies the bug and the actual value of `percentage`?

What is printed as the result of the following code?

```java
int a = 7;
int b = 2;
double c = (double)(a / b);
double d = a / (double) b;
System.out.print(c + " " + d);
```

What is the value of `result` after the following code executes?

```java
int a = 10;
int b = 4;
int c = 6;
double result = (double) a / b + c / b;
```

Determine the values of `x` and `y` after the following code runs.

```java
double x = 7 / 2;
double y = (double) 7 / 2;
```

What is printed by the following code?

```java
int n = Integer.MAX_VALUE;
n = n + 1;
System.out.println(n);
```

Determine the values of `a` and `b` after the following code runs.

```java
double temperature = 98.6;
int a = (int) temperature;
int b = (int)(temperature + 0.5);
```

Determine the output of the following code:

```java
int p = 9;
int q = 4;
double a = p / q;
double b = (double)(p / q);
double c = (double) p / q;
System.out.println(a + " " + b + " \ + c);
```

Determine the value stored in `result` after the following code runs.

```java
int x = 10;
int y = 3;
double result = x / y;
```

Determine the output of the following code.

```java
int a = 17;
int b = 5;
double result = (double)(a / b);
System.out.println(result);
```

Determine the output of the following code.

```java
int a = 5;
int b = 2;
System.out.println(a / b);
System.out.println((double) a / b);
```

What is printed by the following code?

```java
int x = Integer.MAX_VALUE;
x = x + 1;
System.out.println(x);
```

Determine the output of the following code:

```java
int a = 7;
int b = 2;
double x = a / b;
double y = (double) a / b;
int z = (int)(y + 0.5);
System.out.print(x + " " + y + " " + z);
```

Determine the output of the following code:

```java
int n = Integer.MAX_VALUE;
n += 2;
System.out.print(n);
```
